A research project aimed at assisting <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the People 's Bank of China</ENAMEX> in implementing supervision and control of insurance laws and regulations formulated by foreign - capital insurance institutions in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">China</ENAMEX> , and exploring the system and measures for standardizing insurance , was started in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Beijing</ENAMEX> recently .
